### =============================================
### PROJECTS API
### =============================================

### Test API Root
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Lihat Semua Proyek (public — no auth required)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects

### Cari Proyek by Keyword (Search)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects?search=React

### Filter Proyek by Status dan Budget
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects?status=Open&budget_min=4000000&budget_max=10000000

### Dashboard Client: Lihat Proyek Milik Sendiri
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects?mitra_id=1

### Lihat Detail Proyek (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects/1

### Buat Proyek Baru (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

{
  "judul_proyek": "Aplikasi E-Commerce",
  "deskripsi_proyek": "Platform belanja online modern",
  "skills": ["Frontend", "Backend", "Database"],
  "requirements": "Pengalaman dengan React dan Node.js",
  "mitra_id": 1,
  "kuota_maksimal": 3,
  "status_proyek": "Open",
  "budget_awal": 5000000
}

### Update Proyek (requires auth)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

{
  "judul_proyek": "Aplikasi E-Commerce v2",
  "deskripsi_proyek": "Platform belanja online modern (updated)",
  "skills": ["Frontend", "Backend", "Database"],
  "requirements": "React, Node.js, PostgreSQL",
  "budget_awal": 7500000
}

### Hapus Proyek (requires auth)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/projects/1
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client




### =============================================
### BIDDING API
### =============================================

### Buat Bid Baru (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bidding
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: MHS001
X-User-Type: talent

{
  "project_id": 4,
  "group_id": "KLP001",
  "student_id": "MHS001",
  "priority": 1,
  "document_url": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/proposal-sistem.pdf",
  "tawaran_harga": 4500000,
  "tawaran_waktu": "2026-06-20"
}

### Lihat Semua Bid — sebagai Client (otomatis terfilter by proyek miliknya)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bidding
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

### Lihat Semua Bid — sebagai Talent (otomatis terfilter by kelompoknya)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bidding
X-User-ID: KLP001
X-User-Type: talent

### Lihat Detail Bid by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bidding/1
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

### UPDATE STATUS BID (ACCEPT/REJECT) - CRITICAL ENDPOINT WITH DB LOCKING
### Hanya client pemilik proyek atau admin yang bisa akses ini
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/bidding/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

{
  "status": "Accepted"
}





### =============================================
### NEGOTIATING API
### =============================================

### Buat Negosiasi Baru (bid_id di URL param)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: KLP001
X-User-Type: talent

{
  "response_harga": 4200000,
  "response_waktu": "2026-06-25"
}

### Buat Negosiasi — Response dari Client
POST http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

{
  "response_harga": 4350000,
  "response_waktu": "2026-06-22"
}

### Lihat Semua Negosiasi
GET http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

### Lihat Negosiasi per Bid ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/1
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

### UPDATE STATUS NEGOSIASI (FINAL DEAL ACCEPT/REJECT)
### Endpoint ini otomatis sinkronisasi harga/waktu ke tabel bid jika Accepted
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: 1
X-User-Type: client

{
  "status": "Accepted"
}

### Hapus Negosiasi
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/negotiating/
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-ID: KLP001
X-User-Type: talent

{
  "nego_id": 1,
  "bid_id": 1
}
